&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Lead the U.S.-based Benefits &amp;amp; Mobility COE, including the design, administration, and ongoing management of health &amp;amp; welfare, retirement, wellness, leave, and mobility programs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;

