&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Performing in a fast-paced environment, BCMA Commercial Financial Analyst will be supporting our financial planning and analysis (FP&amp;amp;A) activities. This role will involve close collaboration with Legend’s business teams. The ideal candidate possess strong analytical skills with the ability to collect, organize, analyze and disseminate significant amounts of information with attention to detail and accuracy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
